{"article_id":"D6BbZcCIbAPNyeKS","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Authorities ask federal and state agents to help identify two men","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"seen in photos","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"The men are of `` high interest '' in the probe into the Boston Marathon blasts","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"One of the men is seen in photos","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"carrying a black backpack ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"an official says","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"3 people were killed and about 180 injured","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"when 2 bombs went off near the finish line","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Investigators have pinpointed two men as `` possible suspects ''","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"who were seen in images near the finish line of this week 's Boston Marathon","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"-- moments before twin bombs there exploded ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"killing three and injuring about 180 others --","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"a law enforcement official said .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"A circular","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"sent out Wednesday to federal and state agencies","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"features the photos `` in an attempt","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"to identify the individuals , ''","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"who were described as being of `` high interest '' to investigators .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"One of the men is seen","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"carrying a black backpack .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"An FBI official earlier said","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"that authorities believe","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"the bombs were placed inside a black nylon backpack or bag .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"The source said","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that authorities had not yet identified the two men by name","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and that the photographs were not being released to the public for fear","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"of impeding the investigation .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Earlier Wednesday , two official sources with knowledge of the investigation identified a man","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"-- who also has n't been named --","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"as a possible suspect in the attack .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Seen on a video ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"this man wore a white baseball cap .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"One of the sources added","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"that the cap was on backwards","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"and the man was also wearing a light-colored hooded sweatshirt and a black jacket .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"It was not immediately known","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"if this man is one of those","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"alluded to in the photographs","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"distributed to law enforcement officials .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"This movement in the investigation came","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"two days after the horrific blast shook the city ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"during what is traditionally one of its biggest and most beloved events each year .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"By Wednesday , authorities had made `` significant progress '' in the case but no arrests ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"a federal law enforcement source told CNN 's John King .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Sources previously told CNN","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that a suspect was in custody ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"but both Boston police and the FBI denied","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that any arrests had been made .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"A Boston law enforcement source told CNN ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"`` We got him , ''","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"but would n't clarify","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"whether that meant","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"a suspect has been identified or arrested .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Some federal sources said","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"it was even too early to say","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"investigators had identified the suspect ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"but several sources in Boston told CNN","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that they have a clear identification .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"Gov . Patrick :","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"No one in custody","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Gov . Patrick :","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"No one in custody","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"02:27","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Source :","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"Bomb was in pressure cooker","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"Source :","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"Bomb was in pressure cooker","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"02:28","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Tracking suspects in the Boston bombings","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Tracking suspects in the Boston bombings 03:16","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Speaking on CNN 's The Situation Room ,","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Massachusetts Gov . Deval Patrick said","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"investigators were closer to cracking the case `` every hour . ''","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"But he urged patience with the probe .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"`` What I would say","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"and I would ask of everyone","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"is we give law enforcement the space","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"to do their work , ''","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Patrick said .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"`` When they are ready with a complete picture ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"they will tell us what that picture is . ''","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"He added ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"`` I wish","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"they had nailed the perpetrator within minutes of this catastrophe ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"but I understand from experience","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"it 's going to take some time . ''","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Earlier Wednesday , investigators revealed more details about the makeup of the bombs ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"which exploded 12 seconds apart .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"One had been housed in a pressure cooker","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"hidden inside a backpack ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"the FBI said in a joint intelligence bulletin .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"The device also had fragments","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"that may have included nails , BBs and ball bearings ,","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"the agency said .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"The lid of a pressure cooker","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"thought to be used in the device","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"was found on a rooftop at the scene ,","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"a federal law enforcement official with firsthand knowledge of the investigation told CNN .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"The second bomb was also housed in a metal container ,","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"but it was not clear whether it too was in a pressure cooker ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"the FBI said .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"The U.S. government has warned federal agencies in the past","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"that terrorists could turn pressure cookers into bombs","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"by packing them with explosives and shrapnel","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"and detonating them with blasting caps .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Photos","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"obtained by CNN","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"show the remains of a pressure cooker","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"found at the scene ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"along with a shredded black backpack and what appear to be metal pellets or ball bearings .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Scraps of at least one pressure cooker , nails and nylon bags","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"found at the scene","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"were sent to the FBI 's national laboratory in Virginia ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"where technicians will try to reconstruct the devices ,","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"the agent","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"leading the investigation","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"said Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"The pieces suggest","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"each of the devices was 6 liters","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"( about 1.6 gallons )","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"in volume ,","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"a Boston law enforcement source said .","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"The recovered parts include part of a circuit board ,","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"which might have been used","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"to detonate a device .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"A law enforcement official said","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"Monday 's bombs were probably detonated by timers .","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"But the FBI said","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"details of the detonating system were unknown .","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"While the clues moved the investigation forward ,","depth":6},{"id":140,"text":"they did not make it immediately apparent","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"whether the attack was an act of domestic or foreign terrorism .","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"`` If your experience and your expertise is Middle East terrorism ,","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"it has the hallmarks of al Qaeda or a Middle East group , ''","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"former FBI Assistant Director Tom Fuentes said .","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"`` If your experience is domestic groups and bombings","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"that have occurred here ,","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"it has the hallmarks of a domestic terrorist like Eric Rudolph in the 1996 Atlanta Summer Olympics bombings . ''","depth":7},{"id":148,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"Boston doctor :","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"'Everyone was my patient '","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"Boston doctor :","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"'Everyone was my patient '","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"03:19","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"Remembering 8-year-old Martin Richard","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"Remembering 8-year-old Martin Richard","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"02:44","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"Fuentes said","depth":7},{"id":163,"text":"he has investigated both types of terrorism","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"-- from Iraq to the United States --","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"and finds","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"the Boston attack has elements of both .","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"`` It has the hallmarks of both domestic and international","depth":8},{"id":168,"text":"( attacks ) ,","depth":8},{"id":169,"text":"and you can see either side of that . ''","depth":7},{"id":170,"text":"Boston University identified graduate student Lingzi Lu as the third person","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"who died in Monday 's bombings .","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"Previously identified were Krystle Campbell , 29 , of Arlington , Massachusetts , and Martin Richard , 8 , of Dorchester , Massachusetts .","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"`` She was the best , ''","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"Campbell 's distraught mother , Patty , told reporters Tuesday .","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"`` You could n't ask for a better daughter . ''","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"Martin `` was a bright , energetic young boy","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"who had big dreams and high hopes for his future , ''","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"his school said in a statement .","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"`` We are heartbroken by this loss . ''","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"The attack left Boston police with `` the most complex crime scene","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"that we 've dealt with in the history of our department , ''","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"Commissioner Ed Davis said Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"Authorities sifted through thousands of pieces of evidence and a mass of digital photos and video clips .","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"They have pleaded for the public 's help","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"in providing additional leads and images .","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"`` Someone knows","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"who did this , ''","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"said Rick DesLauriers , the special agent in charge of the FBI 's Boston office , said .","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"`` The community will play a crucial role in this investigation . ''","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"Medical personnel","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"treating the wounded","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"found evidence","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"suggesting","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"the bomb maker or bomb makers sought to maximize the suffering .","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"Dr. George Velmahos , head of trauma care at Massachusetts General Hospital , said","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"his team found `` numerous '' metal pellets and nails inside patients ' bodies .","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"`` There are people","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"who have 10 , 20 , 30 , 40 of them in their body , or more , ''","depth":13},{"id":199,"text":"Velmahos said .","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"Dr. Ron Walls also said","depth":11},{"id":201,"text":"one patient had more than 12 carpenter-type nails .","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":"`` There is no question","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"some of these objects were implanted in the device for the purpose","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"of being exploded forward , ''","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"As investigators continued to search for a suspect ,","depth":8},{"id":207,"text":"those wounded in the incident continued to recover .","depth":8},{"id":208,"text":"Boston-area hospitals had released at least 112 of the 178 people","depth":9},{"id":209,"text":"injured in the attack ,","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"according to CNN 's tally late Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":211,"text":"Of the 66 people","depth":10},{"id":212,"text":"who were still hospitalized ,","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"13 were in critical condition .","depth":9},{"id":214,"text":"Boston Medical Center has two patients in critical condition , down from 11 just after the bombings ,","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"Dr. Peter Burke , chief of trauma care , told reporters Wednesday .","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"Ten patients are in serious condition","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"and seven are in fair condition ,","depth":11},{"id":218,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"Spectator Steve Byrne was standing with a group of friends near a mailbox","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"when the second blast went off .","depth":12},{"id":221,"text":"Now his face is scarred with shrapnel wounds .","depth":12},{"id":222,"text":"A BB pellet remains lodged in his neck .","depth":13},{"id":223,"text":"Doctors said","depth":15},{"id":224,"text":"they could n't remove it","depth":16},{"id":225,"text":"because was too close to nerves","depth":17},{"id":226,"text":"that control his vision ,","depth":17},{"id":227,"text":"but he was out of the hospital on Wednesday .","depth":14},{"id":228,"text":"Compared to how his friends are suffering ,","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"he told CNN 's AC360","depth":12},{"id":230,"text":"that he feels lucky .","depth":12},{"id":231,"text":"Four out of the five friends","depth":13},{"id":232,"text":"he was watching the marathon with","depth":13},{"id":233,"text":"have lost limbs ,","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":235,"text":"One friend had 70 nails in his leg .","depth":10},{"id":236,"text":"He remembers the explosion in vivid detail :","depth":11},{"id":237,"text":"the blast","depth":13},{"id":238,"text":"that was so strong","depth":14},{"id":239,"text":"that it burned his clothes off ;","depth":14},{"id":240,"text":"the carnage around him ; and the haunting , slow-motion daze","depth":13},{"id":241,"text":"of searching for his friends .","depth":13},{"id":242,"text":"`` We were having a great day","depth":13},{"id":243,"text":"and waiting to see our friend cross the finish line , ''","depth":13},{"id":244,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":245,"text":"`` and then all of the sudden it turned in a flash . ''","depth":11},{"id":246,"text":"He told CNN","depth":11},{"id":247,"text":"he 's worried about the financial burdens","depth":13},{"id":248,"text":"his friends could face","depth":13},{"id":249,"text":"as a result of the explosion .","depth":12},{"id":250,"text":"One friend is a carpenter","depth":13},{"id":251,"text":"and `` both his hands are incinerated .","depth":14},{"id":252,"text":"He ca n't go to work ,","depth":15},{"id":253,"text":"and the bills keep coming in . '' `` It 's not just the hospitals .","depth":15},{"id":254,"text":"It 's everyday life","depth":13},{"id":255,"text":"that does n't stop . ...","depth":13},{"id":256,"text":"We 're just hoping","depth":12},{"id":257,"text":"the mayor , the governor , President Obama do n't let us as citizens down . ''","depth":12},{"id":258,"text":"Beyond those seriously wounded , the incident affected thousands ,","depth":8},{"id":259,"text":"including Candace Rispoli ,","depth":10},{"id":260,"text":"who was cheering on a friend","depth":11},{"id":261,"text":"when the festive atmosphere turned into a `` terrifying hell . ''","depth":11},{"id":262,"text":"She suffered minor injuries .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":525,"left":0,"right":524,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"pare